    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "you say \"let go of the fight\" like it's some kind of peaceful choice, but it's not. it's just the reality. the noise, the shame, the constant feeling that i'm an intruder in my own life... it's just too much. if there's nothing left to save, then what's the point of dragging this hollow shell around? it feels like the only way to actually find any peace is to just finish it.",
